      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is ISO 9001:2015 certified. The hemolysis UDF library (v2.4.1) is maintained under Git with 94% branch coverage verified by CI pipeline. Code review records for all three UDF modules are archived in the project document management system. Achieved Gradation 4: formal SQA plan in place with documented test suite and version control; Gradation 5 not required as independent third-party audit was not mandated for this submission."
