      },
      "rationale": "SST k-ω selected based on literature review of 12 pump CFD studies; documented as best-performing model for centrifugal pump hemolysis in Pauli et al. (2019) systematic comparison. Hemolysis constants (α=3.62×10⁻⁷, β=2.416, γ=0.785) from Giersiepen et al. (1990) calibrated for blood analog. Alternative model comparison: k-ε RNG predicts hemolysis 8% higher; LES predicts 4% higher at OP3. SST k-ω selected as conservative. Achieved Gradation 4."
